Sentencas: Determining the relationship between electrical conductivity and doping level in high temperature proton conductors is of great significance to accelerate their process of practicality and develop new applications.
Titulo: Electrical conduction behavior of proton conductor BaCe1-xSmxO3-δ in the intermediate temperature range

Sentencas: In this work, BaCe1-xSmxO3-delta (x = 0.01-0.50) was synthesized via citric-nitrate method and their electrical conduction behavior in 5% H-2/Ar in the intermediate temperature range was investigated.
Titulo: Electrical conduction behavior of proton conductor BaCe1-xSmxO3-δ in the intermediate temperature range

Sentencas: The solubility of Sm in BaCeO3 was between 0.30 and 0.40.
Titulo: Electrical conduction behavior of proton conductor BaCe1-xSmxO3-δ in the intermediate temperature range

Sentencas: Both the bulk and the grain boundary conductivity increased with Sm content up to x = 0.20 and then decreased.

Sentencas: The infrared spectra results indicated that the degree of hydrogen bonding decreased with Sm content (x = 0.20-0.30), which should be responsible for the descending bulk conductivity of samples with x = 0.25 and 0.30.
Titulo: Electrical conduction behavior of proton conductor BaCe1-xSmxO3-δ in the intermediate temperature range

Sentencas: BaCe0.80Sm0.20O3-delta, with electrical conductivity of 0.017 S cm(-1) at 600 degrees C, was a promising electrolyte for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells.
